{"tid":89313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"很多學生不願赴京讀書,史丹福大學終止北大交換生計劃","createTime":"2017-01-21T09:13:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T05:49:39.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ecc7dc77b367db9088c36422b4c30c1ff6a38a22","tid":89313,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:13:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/hIGHRC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FhIGHRC.jpg&h=ee2a8e32&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中國向海外輸出軟實力受創？美國名校史丹福大學日前公佈，將自本年度起，無限期終止與北京大學合作十多年的本科交換生計劃（圖），原因是報名率太低，很多學生不願到北京讀書。 <br />\n<br />\n專門報道史丹福大學動態的《Stanford Daily》近日指，該交換生計劃始於2004年，每年提供20至30個名額讓史大的本科生參與。初時參與率高企，名額均能全部填滿；惟近年卻持續下降，至去年春天更只有8人報名參加。校方早前為吸引學生報名，已取消原來普通話作為參加計劃的必要語言要求，惟報讀人數依舊低迷。該校「Bing海外留學計劃」負責人表示，以往的海外交流計劃只要取消當地語言要求，報名率會上升，然而這次卻沒任何效果。 <br />\n<br />\n學生︰安排混亂欠吸引力 <br />\n<br />\n有前年參加計劃赴京的學生稱，感覺計劃安排頗混亂，其中於北京上課時的課堂與設施，與她聽聞其他8個國家的交換生計劃比較，水平明顯有所不及。她更指，讀電腦科學工程的學生傾向赴德國交流，因當地交流附帶實習；對環球服務業有興趣的學生則選南非；而赴京的交流計劃的吸引力相對遜色。據悉該校正尋求在北京以外的中國城市設立交換生計劃，惟暫未有具體詳情。有網民認為，這是對中國海外軟實力的打擊，也有說法稱該校應選霧霾較輕微的中國城市作交流計劃目的地。《Stanford Daily》 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170121/19904258\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170121%2F19904258&d=5K0ufhZAmatzs65nkjOUcmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=45743f97\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170121%2F19904258&h=a82bb6f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170121/19904258</a>"},{"pid":"e262dc9da24be0e882ef3f30173bead48ea5d33d","tid":89313,"uid":71473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:14:09.000Z","msg":"去北京做人體實驗？搵撚去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d623d44d1cbff356542f1b953da0026692b4cf","tid":89313,"uid":74497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉屌,少咗個免費屌黃雞既機會"},{"pid":"b50d13afdc18a4d8374560585fb0b66fe04f1015","tid":89313,"uid":62391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:16:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a0cc8db051b9db699fc8440c6708e1ecc4cfd11","tid":89313,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:16:32.000Z","msg":"去吸毒氣"},{"pid":"0234c174fb6501ebd259a7c331bb422522e77002","tid":89313,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:18:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉屌,少咗個免費屌黃雞既機會</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed52be550e0a585191300e7bbcef0eae8f14249","tid":89313,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:33:56.000Z","msg":"除咗提供免費慰安婦<br />\n對大陸有咩意義"},{"pid":"42d867ee67d3849b8d1448ab7b6abd1bcbcd1b46","tid":89313,"uid":39351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:52:50.000Z","msg":"前排唔係話要脅美國，會大幅減少前往美國嘅留學生？<br />\n咁依家美國幫你手做埋，咪得償所願囉，應該要舉國慶祝。"},{"pid":"2f256557aff20b1ebf0a0903b89f708475051d6e","tid":89313,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:53:49.000Z","msg":"幫手吸毒氣"},{"pid":"e9bdd89e1703d02f4013e201bbcba09fd4cc3850","tid":89313,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:54:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉屌,少咗個免費屌黃雞既機會</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要吸D具中國特色的, 而且年年益壽既霧霾<br />\nd鬼佬真係唔識貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b77e6040d84c9ca4f02961c3da71375841f90c","tid":89313,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:56:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前排唔係話要脅美國，會大幅減